This paper deals with emotion detection from text, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes an architecture inspired by the Mixture of Experts (MoE) model, which is a machine learning technique, indicating that it could also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with feature extraction and classification, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
